{"tid":1475800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[818] 勇武除低豬嘴就係和理非","createTime":"2019-08-15T15:03:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T15:49:46.000Z","uid":67023,"like":71,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7703e1b83591db25414e2f24b8a80c2ca666843f","tid":1475800,"uid":67023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:03:42.000Z","msg":"相信好多勇武手足都會除低豬嘴去遊行同集會，過去兩個月抗爭咗咁耐，我真係好想知道仲有幾多人支持緊我哋<br />\n<br />\n七一之後勇武嘅每次行動和理非都無出嚟阻止，而今次818我希望大家比次機會純和理非遊行，我哋共同將遊行嘅人數推上一個新嘅歷史高位，比佢哋可以係一個自己完全舒適同認同嘅環境下表達佢哋嘅訴求<br />\n<br />\n勇武同和理非之間一定會有好多磨擦同矛盾，而且係使用武力上嘅睇法必定存在差異，但係我哋兩者嘅團結先係今次能夠成功嘅原因之一，我哋兩者係缺一不可。<br />\n<br />\n既然和理非可以體諒我哋使用嘅武力，核爆都唔割，不如我哋今次都體諒一下和理非嘅堅持？就好似星期二機場事件發生之後，我有一刻諗過成場運動會就咁失敗，但係第二日我發覺大家互屌過後都即刻檢討同改善，我真係喊咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋都係想整場運動會成功，呢個係我哋<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人</span>嘅共同目的<br />\n<br />\n最後我想同所有勇武道歉，我唔係想騎劫大家嘅意見，我只係想將自己身為勇武一員嘅睇法講出嚟，希望大家唔好屌得咁大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw帶唔帶gear嘅問題，我會帶定係身，因為班狗已經癲咗，佢哋癲起上嚟唔知會做啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比個機會純和理非<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我會繼續勇武"},{"pid":"775924afca3d49b52993fb2a6a3de4bf70158066","tid":1475800,"uid":67023,"like":46,"dislike":10,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />帶定gear<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔帶gear"},{"pid":"a646ed2ba760b7160e639e16bbe6e75ecea2b64b","tid":1475800,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:04:17.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2c322da9df29c1b463dcb8d3fd8add5a3bc5cd2f","tid":1475800,"uid":56607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:05:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M8KKhws.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM8KKhws.jpg&h=3e32fc8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"969b0decc1715d030d2434b4a1e5a0efd590bf95","tid":1475800,"uid":67023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:06:46.000Z","msg":"啱啱見完老豆，想提下大家<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一定一定</span>要black bloc"},{"pid":"539acb6b6e596b5c343b5c6d3525557ee9e91e0d","tid":1475800,"uid":67223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:07:18.000Z","msg":"毋忘初衷<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山<br />\n各司其職<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n <br />\n612 721 811<br />\n<br />\n818 和理非assemble<br />\n--------------------------------------<br />\n&ldquo;無大台的下一步! 無符號(semiotics)!&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464335\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464335</a>"},{"pid":"6cdc12dc16d47bce6866a68bd5df7c8b14faa5eb","tid":1475800,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:07:27.000Z","msg":"咁地帶唔帶老人細路先？<br />\n<br />\n危險，唔帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個都不能少，帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6567a9c45fc0d7f250d0fba7d3678bad9a4ab2a","tid":1475800,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:07:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vu1TVgv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvu1TVgv.jpg&h=4114d504&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n612 721 805 811<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">816</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: 